{"tid":2090132,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"7.1現身銅鑼灣  王宗堯冀港人：要支持住","createTime":"2020-07-02T04:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T04:21:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4141c2768bba8e25e8b704fe5307ac341df7c3dc","tid":2090132,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:21:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200702/BE4RQMI33M3UIDQGBHSEJ5ZSDU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200702%2FBE4RQMI33M3UIDQGBHSEJ5ZSDU%2F&d=oBn6KkEvnt0QU92xe9ZG8BphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=89abbba2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200702%2FBE4RQMI33M3UIDQGBHSEJ5ZSDU%2F&h=5f3ae471\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200702/BE4RQMI33M3UIDQGBHSEJ5ZSDU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n7.1現身銅鑼灣 <br />\n王宗堯冀港人：要支持住<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港版國安法於昨日7.1實行，大批市民無懼白色恐怖到銅鑼灣崇光購物，王宗堯下午現身渣甸街「渣哥」客串店長，同場還有立法會議員譚文豪及渣哥。被控暴動罪的王宗堯有案在身，保釋期間若再被捕有機會不能再保釋，現身銅鑼灣很高危。王宗堯受訪時指是應渣哥之邀到場幫手：「開心見到今日咁多市民出嚟行街。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鍾鎮濤阿佘表忠賀立法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DYamsOj-EfK5g96L2ncp1ytEKfw=/640x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3FY5MJQ74VLYN5GCNF5ZHZGDEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDYamsOj-EfK5g96L2ncp1ytEKfw%3D%2F640x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3FY5MJQ74VLYN5GCNF5ZHZGDEQ.jpg&h=cb67ad02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被控暴動罪的王宗堯，昨日仍到銅鑼灣，未有擔心自身安全。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i2p__XyWhVjOsBXQdb9i4Xl2Qcw=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LQEQAOZ7BQ4N4VXWQUWREUYBH4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi2p__XyWhVjOsBXQdb9i4Xl2Qcw%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLQEQAOZ7BQ4N4VXWQUWREUYBH4.jpg&h=1c3186c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王宗堯和議員譚文豪（右）昨日幫手睇檔。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">Tommy對太太收到塞紙條恐嚇，他坦言不會因此而收聲。</span><br />\nTommy對太太收到塞紙條恐嚇，他坦言不會因此而收聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTommy無懼恐嚇<br />\n<br />\n談到港版國安法，王宗堯說：「個範圍好似宇宙咁闊，唔擔心得咁多，利物浦都攞冠軍，冇乜係冇可能，香港人一定要支持住。」去年7.1因闖入立法會，早前被加控暴動罪，王宗堯指官司暫排期下月再審，他以平常心應對：「𠵱家個判刑期郁啲就話十年，諗唔到咁多，瞓醒一覺都已經過咗二十幾年喇。」問到會否擔心店舖有被控告風險？渣哥說：「唔擔心，我奉公守法，最支持基本法。」<br />\n<br />\n阮民安（Tommy）太太Eva前晚收恐嚇信，信中提到對Tommy不利：「7.1如果見到你斬X你」，但昨早Tommy坐在維港前於<br />\n。。。。。<br />\n佢哋話乜就乜，所以根本冇得驚。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/FPyaUUIULQY_EP021G1FAIIoyIg=/640x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/K4AY7BYCTJSRJGOFOQ562TLFU4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFPyaUUIULQY_EP021G1FAIIoyIg%3D%2F640x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FK4AY7BYCTJSRJGOFOQ562TLFU4.jpg&h=e2510c30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n杜汶澤在fb留言稱要感謝藍絲或五毛，關心他是否已經死亡或坐監。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wnV1-6vJ-9AHYW95PhOM5CEcSBI=/640x900/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3Y5DEVTY4FVFYGMFEDFU72MMIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwnV1-6vJ-9AHYW95PhOM5CEcSBI%3D%2F640x900%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3Y5DEVTY4FVFYGMFEDFU72MMIA.jpg&h=48c9aca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n何韻詩昨在Ig限時動態貼街頭相，更寫上香港人無懼。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n何韻詩<br />\n何韻詩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBLACK PINK被封手足<br />\n<br />\n此外，敢言的杜汶澤在fb報平安：「我會不時向你們報告情況，如果引起閣下不安<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n骨」。何韻詩昨日黃昏在Ig限時動態上載銅鑼灣街頭相，並寫上：「香港人無懼」。<br />\n<br />\n[img]BLACK PINK成員Ros&eacute;昨日貼由銅鑼灣出發的巴士照片，被網民稱為手足。互聯網圖片[/img]<br />\nBLACK PINK成員Ros&eacute;昨日貼由銅鑼灣出發的巴士照片，被網民稱為手足。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/3qcrNihb2V2znVeY04exP4gETdU=/640x800/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UEVRII4UMH7KLMA56I5THQELWQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F3qcrNihb2V2znVeY04exP4gETdU%3D%2F640x800%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUEVRII4UMH7KLMA56I5THQELWQ.jpg&h=d2c9e551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nRos&eacute;<br />\n<br />\n擅玩二創的填詞人梁栢堅，寸爆警方昨日舉「紫旗」宣告以國安法拉人：「係咪要叫 #除紫旗 #我係fans」。他接受《蘋果》訪問說：「係紫旗都扯，唔扯坐監！」而前DJ詹志文昨日凌晨則感慨白色恐怖：「有人連follow我也不敢了。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，韓國女團BLACK PINK成員Ros&eacute;昨日於Ig限時動態上載其品牌廣告黑白相，廣告中有一架由銅鑼灣出發的城巴962號，被連登仔視為手足。"}]}